board.name: eFinancial Careers
board.description: eFinancialCareers, a Dice Holdings company, serves the global financial community network of career sites for professionals working in banking and the financial markets and those firms seeking to employ them.
board.details:
When Reposting to eFinancial Careers, please do not change Job Title, Job Reference or Location. Other data can be updated.
If you wish to post a new job with new Title, Reference or Location, please use Post from Template option.

rule.message: eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 200 characters in Job Title.
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 100 characters in Salary Text Override.
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 50 characters in Job Reference.
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 400 characters in Optional Summary Override.
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 40 characters in Extra Benefits.
Brand ID has to be numeric
Team ID has to be numeric
Template ID has to be numeric
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 45 words in Optional Summary Override.
eFinancial Careers allow a maximum of 2000 words in Job Description.
